Tested on Emacs 23

Install packages
sudo apt-get install emacs23 emacs-goodies-el pyflakes pep8 pymacs

Make a link from the dotemacs file
ln -s ~/.emacs.d/dotemacs ~/.emacs

Copy pycomplete.py to python path (this works on ubuntu)
sudo cp ~/.emacs.d/pycomplete.py /usr/local/lib/python2.6/dist-packages/